narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Interesting discussion of addictive things. Minimal work for an engaging topic.
Best Econ seminar for Econ majors

I recommend this course as a senior econ seminar. you get to think about really interesting subjects through an econ lens and have interesting discussions. workload: 6ish reading responses, presentation, 10 page paper
